txt.en: 'Waymeet may not seem like much, but some important hobbits come out of here. Just ask around and see if they haven't.'
'I'm so tired of Waymeet...I want to go to Michel Delving.'
'I hope to go to Michel Delving again soon and kick up my heels in the big city!'
Do you know Padric? He asked me to the dance, but I don't know what to wear.'
